":0,"quote":{"pid":"02e0b49cc9438ae6470af56efaeea108aa633c16","tid":705567,"uid":38744,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d940df2fea2cd87b7d1ad91fafa28ba93ab106db","tid":705567,"uid":82450,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T09:17:33.000Z","msg":"你有證據 拎落樓下保安就得"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T09:18:45.000Z","msg":"冇用架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n食Q最多上黎巡兩圈就算"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T09:23:15.000Z","msg":"就係因為你冇證據<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我上次樓上勁嘈幾日成朝啪啪聲 我即刻錄音投訴 之後跟保安逐間屋拍門了解 又出埋通告話會扣分點點點 之後就冇事了"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T09:36:08.000Z","msg":"你冇事係因為比你投訴一戶人淆底姐<br />\n其實如果佢照嘈都吹佢唔漲<br />\n因為好難捉,而且房署主任都懶得去捉<br />\n佢要房署主任親自上到去巡果陣聽到噪音<br />\n而且要100%肯定係由果一個單位傳出黎佢先出到警告信<br />\n再犯先會扣分<br />\n<br />\n而多數情況既住戶見到有房署既人上到去都會收左聲,所以房署就可以話冇噪音,只會勸一勸了事<br />\n而你個所謂證據係冇用<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr17-18/chinese/panels/hg/papers/hg20180507cb1-894-1-c.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.legco.gov.hk%2Fyr17-18%2Fchinese%2Fpanels%2Fhg%2Fpapers%2Fhg20180507cb1-894-1-c.pdf&d=RfqEjC4p9oIoQvPbz36vO8mDuOf2Rd%2FwnGcLKIjXoko%3D&h=737e800c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr17-18/chinese/panels/hg/papers/hg20180507cb1-894-1-c.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n自己睇下扣分制實行左十幾年<br />\n先得165個警告,112個扣分<br />\n平均一年10個<br />\n但全港有70幾萬個單位<br />\n警告同扣分比例咁低就知幾難捉"},{"pid":"0d9b046fbc30725ce51012d36e108523e95811f5","tid":705567,"uid":124797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T13:19:09.000Z","msg":"甘我可以點做？"},{"pid":"4d6b2da87de55c2eba5a347060a76a68410171e6","tid":705567,"uid":9633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0d9b046fbc30725ce51012d36e108523e95811f5","tid":705567,"uid":124797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T13:19:09.000Z","msg":"甘我可以點做？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T13:19:16.000Z","msg":"不停報警？"}]}